text: Amazing blinds really ... Reasonable price and good quality price for my kitchen and bedrooms. Highly recommended

Had a breeze experience dealing with Dennis and spouse. They gave us alot options and advised to ensure the roller blinds fit nicely to our windows and balcony. Even the selection and type of blind's material to choose from to suite our house ambient.
Prices is very affordable to compare with others. I strongly recommend this seller to other who wish to do roller blind in their house. Big cheers to you, Dennis, Spouse and teams.
So easy to deal with. Friendly and professional. Also shared their professional opinion on which material type and colour suits your window / interior.  Very pleased with the service. üëçüëç
